<refnamediv><refname>imvideoprops</refname><refpurpose>Return common OpenCV video capture property IDs.</refpurpose></refnamediv>
<refsynopsisdiv><title>Syntax</title><synopsis>props = imvideoprops()</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv>
<refsection><title>Description</title><para><function>imvideoprops</function> returns a struct of common OpenCV video capture property IDs.</para></refsection>
<refsection><title>Examples</title><programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[
props = imvideoprops();
disp(props.frame_width);
]]></programlisting></refsection>
